  </paragraphs> -->


  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="synthesis-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Read the story together.</li>
      <li>Act out the story as a class using either concrete objects or pictures, whichever was not done during the previous lesson.</li>
    </ul>
  </paragraphs>


